  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526930/extras/32bee34ec81d094765b45aa86e09ad93.avif?t=1729520319\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>PolyCore Defense is a classic tower defense game that is all about the right decisions. In order to succeed you need to pick the right turrets and place them at the most optimal locations. Upgrade your turrets with modules to destroy your enemies faster and counter their abilities. The maps increase in difficulty with shorter and increased number of paths. Can you beat them all?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526930/extras/b4da72f117ed60ebda7dce6cd2bd564a.poster.avif?t=1729520319\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526930/extras/b4da72f117ed60ebda7dce6cd2bd564a.webm?t=1729520319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526930/extras/b4da72f117ed60ebda7dce6cd2bd564a.mp4?t=1729520319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526930/extras/a03e52d7826cc57e363b188570080e56.avif?t=1729520319\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>Use your imagination to build an effective line of defense against waves of enemies with increasing difficulty. Pick and place turrets from your arsenal. Upgrade turrets with modules that enhance them with unique effects. Activate abilities in clutch situations or when you need a little defensive boost.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526930/extras/5cd88e83dacb44ef4748e3f0c312d7c5.poster.avif?t=1729520319\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526930/extras/5cd88e83dacb44ef4748e3f0c312d7c5.webm?t=1729520319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526930/extras/5cd88e83dacb44ef4748e3f0c312d7c5.mp4?t=1729520319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526930/extras/19d0eb8f822369f04bdd1b8e0c986ed7.poster.avif?t=1729520319\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526930/extras/19d0eb8f822369f04bdd1b8e0c986ed7.webm?t=1729520319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526930/extras/19d0eb8f822369f04bdd1b8e0c986ed7.mp4?t=1729520319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526930/extras/70cd7031a9ec01c9cbd23b0e91f7bbce.poster.avif?t=1729520319\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526930/extras/70cd7031a9ec01c9cbd23b0e91f7bbce.webm?t=1729520319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526930/extras/70cd7031a9ec01c9cbd23b0e91f7bbce.mp4?t=1729520319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526930/extras/34db9ef109163001270c0fd0990d6527.avif?t=1729520319\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>Destroy enemies to earn XP and unlock turrets, upgrade modules, perks and abilities. Complete maps to unlock the next one. If you are up for a challenge, try to complete a map without The Core losing any health in order to Ace it. Ace them all for the ultimate challenge!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526930/extras/77256e9405e9e6120f226fecdc15b32d.avif?t=1729520319\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526930/extras/9c3309f5bf556cda07f9a461614970cc.avif?t=1729520319\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526930/extras/e6208379476f82e9581bb2429dbf8c1b.avif?t=1729520319\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Strategic </strong>gameplay<br></li><li> Lots of <strong>unique turrets</strong><br></li><li> Loads of <strong>modules</strong> to <strong>upgrade turrets</strong> in unique ways<br></li><li> Unlockable <strong>abilities</strong><br></li><li> <strong>Leveling</strong> system<br></li><li> <strong>Endless mode</strong>, how long will you last?<br></li><li> <strong>Perks</strong> for long term progression<br></li><li> <strong>Various enemies</strong> with different effects<br></li><li> Steam <strong>Achievements</strong><br></li><li> Steam <strong>Leaderboard</strong><br></li><li> Gameplay <strong>Stats</strong><br></li><li> <strong>Challenging</strong> maps<br></li><li> Complete maps without losing any health to ace them for increased challenge</li></ul>",
